OL,3,CITV gain intimate access to the
OL,4,CVardys' Italy relocation for new series
OL,6,FITV will be broadcasting a new series
OL,7,Fabout Jamie and Rebekah Vardy's new
OL,8,Flife in Italy after 13 years at
OL,9,FLeicester City.
OL,11,F'The Vardys' follows the couple and
OL,12,Ftheir four children as they start a
OL,13,Fnew life abroad, and will stream later
OL,14,Fthis year on ITVX and broadcast on
OL,15,FITV1.
OL,17,FIt will cover the fallout of Jamie's
OL,18,Ffinal match at the club and focuses
OL,19,Fheavily on Rebekah's journey as she
OL,20,Fmoves her family abroad.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
