FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1776942175
OL,3,CITV gain intimate access to the
OL,4,CVardys' Italy relocation for new series
OL,6,FShe deals with the emotional and
OL,7,Fphysical upheaval of her new life, and
OL,8,Freflects on her recent challenges in
OL,9,Fthe UK, as she puts the "Wagatha"
OL,10,Fdrama behind her.
OL,12,FThe series follows all the drama and
OL,13,Fchaos of their new family adventure -
OL,14,Ffrom frantic house-hunts and tearful
OL,15,Fschool searches, to unexpected
OL,16,Fdisasters and dramatic setbacks, all
OL,17,Fwhile Jamie battles to prove his
OL,18,Fdoubters wrong on the pitch at the age
OL,19,Fof 38, with Italian side US Cremonese.
OL,26,@qD@YOUqD@aO]
