OL,3,CITV gain intimate access to the
OL,4,CVardys' Italy relocation for new series
OL,6,FITV describe it as a "rollercoaster
OL,7,Fjourney of resilience, fierce family
OL,8,Fbonds, and the promise of a new life."
OL,10,FITV says: "Witness the banter, the
OL,11,Fbickering and the sheer
OL,12,Funpredictability of the Vardys as they
OL,13,Fnavigate cultural clashes, forge new
OL,14,Ffriendships, and make Italy their home.
OL,16,F"Can Jamie rekindle his underdog
OL,17,Fmagic? Will Rebekah find peace and a
OL,18,Fnew purpose away from the glare of the
OL,19,FBritish tabloids? And will the Vardy
OL,20,Ffamily finally find their happily ever
OL,21,Fafter?"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
