PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1776942175
OL,3,CITV gain intimate access to the
OL,4,CVardys' Italy relocation for new series
OL,6,FLouise Major, the Commissioning Editor
OL,7,Ffor Entertainment & Reality, says:
OL,8,F"We're thrilled to be working with the
OL,9,FVardys on this series for ITV1 and
OL,10,FITVX.
OL,12,F"At a pivotal moment in their lives,
OL,13,Fthis is a rare and revealing look
OL,14,Fbehind the headlines ` from the highs
OL,15,Fof Jamie's football legacy to the
OL,16,Frealities of starting over as a
OL,17,Ffamily, with Rebekah sharing her
OL,18,Freflections on one of the most talked-
OL,19,Fabout stories of the last decade."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
