OL,3,CITV gain intimate access to the
OL,4,CVardys' Italy relocation for new series
OL,6,FDan Grabiner and Nat Lippiett,
OL,7,FExecutive Producers for Orchard
OL,8,FStudios say: "The Vardys are an iconic
OL,9,Fand brilliantly entertaining family,
OL,10,Fand this behind-the-scenes insight
OL,11,Finto their big move shows them as
OL,12,Fyou've never seen them before: candid,
OL,13,Funfiltered and completely
OL,14,Funpredictable. Welcome to the Vardy
OL,15,Fparty."
OL,17,FThe Vardys is an Orchard Studios
OL,18,Fproduction for ITV1 and ITVX.
